\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Início\",\"item\":\"https://elementgroup.pt\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Blog\",\"item\":\"https://elementgroup.pt/blog\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"Como manter as redes ativas sem perder o dia nisso\",\"item\":\"https://elementgroup.pt/blog/redes-ativas-sem-perder-tempo\"}]}</script><article><header class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-bg pt-36 pb-10 px-6\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute top-10 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[680px] h-[420px] pointer-events-none\" style=\"background:radial-gradient(circle at 50% 30%, rgba(127,168,217,0.13), transparent 62%)\"></div><div class=\"relative max-w-[760px] mx-auto\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-muted hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/blog\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\">←</span> Blog</a><div class=\"mt-6 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"rounded-full border border-accent/30 bg-accent/10 px-2.5 py-0.5 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-accent font-medium\">Social Media</span><span class=\"text-[11px] text-dark\">4 de junho de 2026<!-- --> · <!-- -->4<!-- --> min de leitura</span></div><h1 class=\"mt-4 text-white tracking-[-0.03em] leading-[1.05]\">Como manter as redes ativas sem perder o dia nisso</h1><p class=\"mt-5 text-muted text-lg leading-relaxed\">Presença consistente não exige horas por dia — exige sistema. Eis o meu.</p><div class=\"mt-7 flex items-center gap-3\"><img alt=\"Ricardo Jorge\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full object-cover object-top border border-white/10\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fricardo-portrait.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fricardo-portrait.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fricardo-portrait.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"text-sm\"><p class=\"text-white leading-tight\">Ricardo Jorge</p><p class=\"text-[11px] text-dark\">Fundador · Element Group</p></div></div></div></header><div class=\"px-6\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-[#101216] max-w-[900px] mx-auto h-52 md:h-72 rounded-[24px] border border-white/10\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#9ec3ea]/30 to-[#4f7fb8]/10\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.12]\" style=\"background-image:radial-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.5) 1px, transparent 1px);background-size:18px 18px\"></div><span class=\"absolute bottom-3 right-4 font-heading font-semibold text-white/10 text-2xl md:text-3xl tracking-tight\">Social Media</span></div></div><div class=\"px-6 py-14\"><div class=\"max-w-[700px] mx-auto\"><p class=\"text-muted leading-relaxed my-4\">O erro mais comum nas redes de um negócio não é publicar mal — é publicar a espaços. Três posts numa semana, depois um mês de silêncio. Quem te visita fica sem saber se ainda existes.</p><h2 class=\"text-white font-heading text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium tracking-[-0.01em] mt-10 mb-3\">Consistência ganha à perfeição</h2><p class=\"text-muted leading-relaxed my-4\">Mais vale um post simples todas as semanas do que um post perfeito de vez em quando. O algoritmo (e os teus clientes) premeiam quem aparece com regularidade.</p><h2 class=\"text-white font-heading text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium tracking-[-0.01em] mt-10 mb-3\">O sistema em três passos</h2><ul class=\"my-4 flex flex-col gap-2.5\"><li class=\"flex gap-3 text-muted leading-relaxed\"><span class=\"mt-2 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>Planeia o mês de uma vez: um calendário com temas evita o bloqueio do “o que publico hoje?”.</li><li class=\"flex gap-3 text-muted leading-relaxed\"><span class=\"mt-2 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>Cria em lote: faz vários posts de seguida em vez de um por dia.</li><li class=\"flex gap-3 text-muted leading-relaxed\"><span class=\"mt-2 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>Agenda e esquece: deixa tudo programado e liberta a tua cabeça.</li></ul><h2 class=\"text-white font-heading text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium tracking-[-0.01em] mt-10 mb-3\">Ou então delega</h2><p class=\"text-muted leading-relaxed my-4\">Se nem isto te apetece, é exatamente para isso que existe a gestão de redes: tu aprovas, eu trato do resto. As redes ativas, sem te roubarem o dia.</p></div></div><div class=\"px-6 pb-16\"><div class=\"max-w-[760px] mx-auto rounded-[24px] border border-accent/30 bg-accent/[0.05] p-8 md:p-10 text-center\"><h2 class=\"text-white font-heading text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium tracking-[-0.01em]\">Gostas do que lês? Posso ajudar-te a aplicá-lo.</h2><p class=\"mt-3 text-muted text-sm max-w-md mx-auto leading-relaxed\">Se quiseres pôr isto a funcionar no teu negócio, é só falares comigo — sem compromisso.</p><div class=\"mt-7 flex justify-center\"><a class=\"nova-btn font-body \" href=\"/servicos/social\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"nova-btn__glow\"></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"nova-btn__ring\"></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"nova-btn__shine\"></span><span class=\"nova-btn__label\">Ver o serviço de Social Media</span></a></div></div></div><section class=\"bg-bg border-t border-white/10 px-6 py-16\"><div class=\"max-w-[1100px] mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"text-white font-heading text-xl font-medium tracking-[-0.01em] mb-8\">Continua a ler</h2><div class=\"grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6\"><a class=\"group flex flex-col rounded-[20px] border border-white/10 bg-bg-card overflow-hidden transition-colors hover:border-white/25\" href=\"/blog/seo-local-top-3-google-maps\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-[#101216] h-36\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/30 to-[#2f4f7a]/10\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.12]\" style=\"background-image:radial-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.5) 1px, transparent 1px);background-size:18px 18px\"></div><span class=\"absolute bottom-3 right-4 font-heading font-semibold text-white/10 text-2xl md:text-3xl tracking-tight\">SEO</span></div><div class=\"p-6\"><span class=\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-accent/90\">SEO</span><h3 class=\"mt-2 text-white font-heading text-base font-medium leading-snug\">SEO local: como chegar ao Top 3 do Google Maps</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-[11px] text-dark\">20 de junho de 2026<!-- --> · <!-- -->6<!-- --> min</p></div></a><a class=\"group flex flex-col rounded-[20px] border border-white/10 bg-bg-card overflow-hidden transition-colors hover:border-white/25\" href=\"/blog/velocidade-site-perder-clientes\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-[#101216] h-36\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#7FA8D9]/30 to-[#1c2738]/10\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.12]\" style=\"background-image:radial-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.5) 1px, transparent 1px);background-size:18px 18px\"></div><span class=\"absolute bottom-3 right-4 font-heading font-semibold text-white/10 text-2xl md:text-3xl tracking-tight\">Websites</span></div><div class=\"p-6\"><span class=\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-accent/90\">Websites</span><h3 class=\"mt-2 text-white font-heading text-base font-medium leading-snug\">A velocidade do teu site está a custar-te clientes</h3><p class=\"mt-3 text-[11px] text-dark\">12 de junho de 2026<!-- --> · <!-- -->5<!-- --> min</p></div></a><a class=\"group flex flex-col rounded-[20px] border border-white/10 bg-bg-card overflow-hidden transition-colors hover:border-white/25\" href=\"/blog/presenca-online-pme-por-onde-comecar\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-[#101216] h-36\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#6f93c4]/30 to-[#0f1318]/10\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.12]\" style=\"background-image:radial-